Balance Receipt — Booking #<%= @appointment.id.to_s.rjust(6, "0") %>
=============================================================

Hi <%= @customer.name %>,

The remaining balance for your appointment with <%= @stylist.name %> has been charged.

Payment successful — <%= number_to_currency(@balance_paid) %> charged to your card on file.

Receipt Details:
  Stylist:        <%= @stylist.name %>
<% if @selected_service.present? %>  Service:        <%= @selected_service %>
<% end %><% if @appointment.appointment_add_ons.any? %>  Add-ons:        <%= @appointment.appointment_add_ons.map(&:service_name).join(", ") %>
<% end %><% if @appointment.location.present? %>  Location:       <%= @appointment.location.name %>
<% end %>  Date & Time:    <%= format_datetime(@appointment.time) %>
  Balance Charged: <%= number_to_currency(@balance_paid) %>
<% if @balance_payment_id.present? %>  Transaction ID: <%= @balance_payment_id %>
<% end %><% if @appointment.completed_at.present? %>  Date Charged:   <%= @appointment.completed_at.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p") %>
<% end %>  Booking #:      #<%= @appointment.id.to_s.rjust(6, "0") %>

View your receipt: <%= balance_receipt_appointment_url(@appointment) %>

